In a message dated 4/5/2003 9:57:26 AM Eastern Standard Time,
anns@... writes:

> OK...I didn't save the conference info, thinking it was not possible, but
> now I'm interested. Please someone show me the way to the info. It still
> may not be possible, but now I want to find out!
> Thank you!
> Ann
> In MI, a day's drive away from SC

http://www.schoolsoutsupport.org/events.html

There are limited work scholarships available---we don't want someone to miss
out because of lack of funds. Check out the Scholarships page.

There is also a message forum for the conference to help you arrange
transportation/carpools and shared lodging. Check it out!

I hope we'll see you then!

~Kelly
